# Production / preview: set in Vercel → your project → Settings → Environment Variables
# (Production, Preview, and/or Development as needed). NEXT_PUBLIC_* are inlined at build time.
# For local dev, copy to `.env.local` or set in your shell.

# NEXT_PUBLIC_CONTACT_EMAIL=you@example.com

# Optional: force asset base path (Vercel and most hosts default to root "").
# NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_PATH=
